        <updateDate>2021-04-22T16:24:19Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Universal Giving Pandemic Response and Recovery Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows individual taxpayers who do not otherwise itemize their tax deductions a deduction in taxable years beginning in 2021 or 2022 for charitable contributions. The deduction is limited to one-third of the standard deduction allowed to such taxpayers. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
